net.varkhan.base.containers.map
Interface Double2FloatMap

All Superinterfaces:
Container<Map.Entry<java.lang.Double,java.lang.Float>>, java.lang.Iterable, Map<java.lang.Double,java.lang.Float>, Searchable<java.lang.Double>, Visitable<Map.Entry<java.lang.Double,java.lang.Float>>
public interface Double2FloatMap
extends Map<java.lang.Double,java.lang.Float>

A searchable container that associates keys to values, and does not allow duplicate keys.

An indexed map of objects, that associates with each unique key an entry, constituted of a modifiable value.
